---

### 🧪 About Me

- 👨‍🔬 Passionate about structural biology, small-angle X-ray scattering (SAXS), and advanced beamline technologies  
- 📚 Committed to sharing knowledge and developing accessible learning tools for the next generation of scatterers  
- 🛠️ Helping shape a more open, reproducible future for structural biology — one scattering curve at a time   

